Last year marked many more milestones for the label with artists like Deorro, Clockwork, Dimitri Vegas & Like Mike, Felix Cartal, Dirtyphonics, Keys N Krates, Coone, Angger Dimas, and Borgore coming to the forefront. The 'Dim Mak Greatest Hits 2013: Remixes' features all of these talented artists and more all in one package, summarizing a very memorable year for Dim Mak.
